                "- Use multiple MeshStandardMaterial zones per hero asset: matte fabric / rough polymer / semi-gloss painted metal / small emissive trims.",
                "- Avoid primitive placeholder reads: even fallback procedural assets need silhouette breaks, bevels, layered attachments, and distinct material separation.",
                "Animation / feel rules:",
                "- Camera orbit must feel damped, readable, and non-mirrored.",
                "- Weapon firing should show cadence, recoil, hit flash, and readable impact feedback.",
