                    + f"发布 **{len(file_names)}** 个文件到预览服务器"
                    + (f",状态:{loaded_status}" if has_preview else "")
                    + "。\n",
                    (f"**Preview URL** · `{preview_url}`\n\n" if preview_url else "")
                    + f"Published **{len(file_names)}** files to preview server"
